Map068.Event[94].Page[0].list.message[2]: "Hah! I guess I misjudged you previously!"
Map068.Event[94].Page[0].list.message[4]: "They say these are the intestines of the god of the depths."
Map068.Event[94].Page[0].list.message[5]: "That means we are inside an older god! Can you believe it?"
Map068.Event[94].Page[0].list.message[6]: "Would you like to join my party?"
"Have you found what you are looking for?"
Map068.Event[94].Page[0].list.message[7]: "Ja. She is not that well known god as most of the time she
spends her days with those forsaken and forgotten."
Map068.Event[94].Page[0].list.message[8]: "Her people often shy away from light."
Map068.Event[94].Page[0].list.message[9]: "That's the case here too. You've seen the cavedwellers?"
Map068.Event[94].Page[0].list.message[10: "The god of the depths is responsible for the layout of
these dungeons. She is ever-changing her shape to challenge
Map068.Event[94].Page[0].list.message[11: "I'd try to please her, if I were to delve deeper."
Map068.Event[94].Page[0].list.message[12: "Hmm... To be honest. My verdict on you is still open."
Map068.Event[94].Page[0].list.message[13: "I don't trust you to put it bluntly."
Map068.Event[94].Page[0].list.message[14: "Your party seems big enough as it is."
Map068.Event[94].Page[0].list.message[15: "I don't like packs of too big in size."
Map068.Event[94].Page[0].list.message[17: "There is a man imprisoned somewhere in these dungeons."
Map068.Event[94].Page[0].list.message[18: "The man has something that shouldn't belong to any human.
Map068.Event[94].Page[0].list.message[19: "And perhaps get rid of the man while at it... He carries
an omnious energy with him. I'm not sure what to think of
